Definition: a lightweight consumer electronic device that looks like a hand-held computer but instead performs specific tasks
Example: can serve as a diary or a personal database or a telephone or an alarm clock etc.
Synonyms: PDA, personal_organizer, personal_organiser, organizer, verb, change, organize, organiser, electronic_device, a, lightweight, consumer, electronic, device, that, looks, like, hand-held, computer, but, instead, performs, specific, tasks, can, serve, as, diary, or, personal, database, telephone, an, alarm, clock, etc
Category: noun.artifact
